column5: Hello Everybody  I hope to catch all the people on right now My cousins husband in Nova Scotia is vying for the prize in the Kraft Hockey Town contest This guy is a straight shooter and dedicated in his pusuits 100 percent Nobody here owes me a thing there is only a few hours left and if you could vote for him it would be very COOL!!!! here is a link to his bio on the Kraft site you can vote there  http://www.krafthockeygoeson.ca/en/nominate/profile/571/   THANKS PETER  :worthy:
Thanks guys for helping out  you guys are great
